# Unity meta files are committed in full.
# A UPM package installed via a git URL is treated as immutable; if any .meta is
# missing Unity regenerates it inside the read-only cache and raises
# "immutable packages were unexpectedly altered", which destabilises the package
# (Editor menus fail to register). Tracking every .meta keeps git installs clean.

# Visual Studio / MonoDevelop generated
.vs/
.vscode/
*.csproj
*.sln
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.suo
*.user
*.unityproj
*.booproj

# OS generated
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
# Worker temp render timelines (WorkerRenderTimelineFactory - worker-recorder-redesign)
_DistRecorder_Temp/
_DistRecorder_Temp.meta
